com.liferay.docs.guestbook.service.base

Class GuestbookServiceBaseImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.liferay.portal.service.BaseServiceImpl
      • com.liferay.docs.guestbook.service.base.GuestbookServiceBaseImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.liferay.docs.guestbook.service.GuestbookService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.bean.IdentifiableBean, com.liferay.portal.service.BaseService, com.liferay.portal.service.InvokableService
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuestbookServiceImpl

    public abstract class GuestbookServiceBaseImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.service.BaseServiceImpl
implements com.liferay.docs.guestbook.service.GuestbookService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.bean.IdentifiableBean
    Provides the base implementation for the guestbook remote service.

    This implementation exists only as a container for the default service methods generated by ServiceBuilder. All custom service methods should be put in GuestbookServiceImpl.

    Author:
    benyedai
    See Also:
    GuestbookServiceImpl, GuestbookServiceUtil
